cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CR 

The paper deals with training deep neural networks and addressing the issue of overfitting noisy examples. This falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also proposes a novel training method, which involves ensemble learning, which is a popular technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the paper discusses the issue of annotation noise, which is a common problem in computer security (cs.CR).
